stateDiagram-v2
  direction LR
  [*] --> raw : ES document polled
  raw --> normalized : source mapper
  normalized --> enriched : GeoIP + MITRE + cloud
  enriched --> deduplicated : dedup_key match?
  deduplicated --> whitelisted : trusted IP/domain
  deduplicated --> active : new alert stored
  whitelisted --> [*] : suppressed
  active --> processed : correlated into incident
  processed --> archived : incident resolved
  archived --> [*]
  note right of active
    status field: active | processed | archived
  end note
